  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Toss borlotti beans with 1 tablespoon of olive oil, salt, and black pepper on a baking sheet and roast for 20 minutes or until tender.",
    "Meanwhile, combine crushed tomatoes, balsamic vinegar, and honey in a bowl. ",
    "In a large bowl, combine roasted borlotti beans, tomato mixture, and chopped basil. ",
    "Cubed bread should be toasted in a pan with the last 2 tablespoons of olive oil until lightly browned. ",
    "Add bread to the bowl and toss gently to combine.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning as needed."
